\n", "last_modified": 1679718037, "replies": 27, "id": 927059}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_large.png?m=1678403810", "name": "vps", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_normal.png?m=1678403810", "title": "VPS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/vps", "topics": 6369, "footer": "", "header": "关于 VPS 购买和使用的讨论。", "title_alternative": "VPS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_mini.png?m=1678403810", "stars": 2965, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 653, "parent_node_name": "cloud"}, "member": {"id": 611410, "username": "hxlgg01", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hxlgg01", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5cbcd52c280e4daf74f106055338d6e3?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5cbcd52c280e4daf74f106055338d6e3?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5cbcd52c280e4daf74f106055338d6e3?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1674895264, "last_modified": 1679545106}, "last_reply_by": "lux182", "last_touched": 1679707501, "title": "有没有便宜的 vps？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926971", "created": 1679664230, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近想玩玩自建 v2 ，请问有没有月付少于 10 块钱或等于 10 块钱的 vps ？", "content_rendered": "<p>最近想玩玩自建 v2 ，请问有没有月付少于 10 块钱或等于 10 块钱的 vps ？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679664230, "replies": 26, "id": 926971}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1614702882", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1614702882", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 1041, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882", "stars": 1481, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 360058, "username": "JavenXiao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/JavenXiao", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c8b/a933/360058_mini.png?m=1676889500", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c8b/a933/360058_normal.png?m=1676889500", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c8b/a933/360058_large.png?m=1676889500", "created": 1541034429, "last_modified": 1676889500}, "last_reply_by": "systemcall", "last_touched": 1679749033, "title": "折腾了很久我发现，我的需求并不需要一台 NAS 来完成", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/927088", "created": 1679727830, "deleted": 0, "content": "买 nas 的主要原因就是为了自建影视库，不希望观影范围局限在审查之内。\r\n\r\n冲配置和颜值买了绿联云，回来就 docker 走起，qbittorrent + plex 走起。\r\n\r\n后来买了块 16T 的企业盘，放在绿联云里吵的要死，跟隔壁装修一样，于是就拆下来装到了台式机上。\r\n\r\n后来试了下在台式机上也装了 qbittorrent + plex ，现在发现这样好像就能满足我的需求了，nas 的优势可能就在于能更省电一丢丢了。", "content_rendered": "<p>买 nas 的主要原因就是为了自建影视库，不希望观影范围局限在审查之内。</p>\n<p>冲配置和颜值买了绿联云，回来就 docker 走起，qbittorrent + plex 走起。</p>\n<p>后来买了块 16T 的企业盘，放在绿联云里吵的要死，跟隔壁装修一样，于是就拆下来装到了台式机上。</p>\n<p>后来试了下在台式机上也装了 qbittorrent + plex ，现在发现这样好像就能满足我的需求了，nas 的优势可能就在于能更省电一丢丢了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679727830, "replies": 23, "id": 927088}]